creator: ForFarming
descriptionHtml:
** Startup Of The Year 2020 ** — Global Startup Awards
** Selected to 2019, 2020, 2021 List ** — The FoodTech 500
Do you want to produce more efficient plants?

Meet Farmi - Solve plant problems with Farmi 24/7. It diagnoses diseases from plant photos and suggests the most suitable solution for you. Farmi improves plant production conditions.

WHAT IS FARMI?
- Farmi is your plant doctor with artificial intelligence support that allows your plants to grow in the most sensitive and efficient way. Farmi is always with you with complete and plant-specific solutions for your plant cultivation.

OUR SOLUTION INCLUDES THE FOLLOWING FEATURES

- Diagnose Sources of Diseases, Pests and Stress
If you have observed any problems with your plants, you can take advantage of this feature by uploading photos of your plants to the system to find out what the problem is and how it can be solved. Our artificial intelligence-supported image processing algorithm will analyze the images you send to detect the problem and recommend the appropriate solutions from the database to you. Our agricultural experts will confirm and forward these results to you within 24 hours.

- Optimize Your Plant Growing Processes
You can get advice on how to improve these conditions so that plants grow faster and healthier by selecting the type of your crop and the current environmental conditions from the system.

- How Will I Grow Plants?
You have started plant production but do not know what to do?
Basic growing conditions are waiting for you in our Farmi library. Growing tips for beginners are in our library.

- Farmi is Your Digital Assistant
You followed the tips, identified the problems, do you need more? You can ask any questions to our experts and you can grow your plants in a controlled manner with their expert opinions.

- Calendar Feature
Thanks to our calendar feature, you can record your production processes, track development processes daily with data and photos. You can also save your to-do list to your calendar and receive reminders. With this way, you can fully complete your tasks and fully implement the plant recipes.



Exclusive Features:
- Special Production Recipes for Your Plants
- 24-Hour Digital Assistant
- Add Unlimited Photos
- Production Planning
- Detection of Diseases from Photos with Artificial Intelligence


* Subscription payouts will be charged to your App Store account upon confirmation of your purchase. Subscriptions will be automatically renewed and you will be charged unless auto-renewal is turned off or you cancel at least 24 hours before the end of the current subscription or trial period. When you purchase a premium subscription during the free trial period, the unused portion of the free trial period is forfeited. The cost of renewal depends on the Subscription Plan you have chosen.
* Subscriptions and automatic renewal can be managed by going to the Account Settings after the purchase or by contacting Customer Support.



Our Standard Subscription Plans:
* 1-week Subscription
* 1-month Subscription
* 1-year Subscription


For full access to all Farmi features, you must allow access to the following:
* Camera – for identifying plants;
* Gallery - to upload images for plant recognition;
* Notifications - To receive plant care reminders.

descriptionHtml:
** Startup Of The Year 2020 ** — Global Startup Awards
** Selected to 2019, 2020, 2021 List ** — The FoodTech 500
Do you want to produce more efficient plants?

Meet Farmi - Solve plant problems with Farmi 24/7. It diagnoses diseases from plant photos and suggests the most suitable solution for you. Farmi improves plant production conditions.

WHAT IS FARMI?
- Farmi is your plant doctor with artificial intelligence support that allows your plants to grow in the most sensitive and efficient way. Farmi is always with you with complete and plant-specific solutions for your plant cultivation.

OUR SOLUTION INCLUDES THE FOLLOWING FEATURES

- Diagnose Sources of Diseases, Pests and Stress
If you have observed any problems with your plants, you can take advantage of this feature by uploading photos of your plants to the system to find out what the problem is and how it can be solved. Our artificial intelligence-supported image processing algorithm will analyze the images you send to detect the problem and recommend the appropriate solutions from the database to you. Our agricultural experts will confirm and forward these results to you within 24 hours.

- Optimize Your Plant Growing Processes
You can get advice on how to improve these conditions so that plants grow faster and healthier by selecting the type of your crop and the current environmental conditions from the system.

- How Will I Grow Plants?
You have started plant production but do not know what to do?
Basic growing conditions are waiting for you in our Farmi library. Growing tips for beginners are in our library.

- Farmi is Your Digital Assistant
You followed the tips, identified the problems, do you need more? You can ask any questions to our experts and you can grow your plants in a controlled manner with their expert opinions.

- Calendar Feature
Thanks to our calendar feature, you can record your production processes, track development processes daily with data and photos. You can also save your to-do list to your calendar and receive reminders. With this way, you can fully complete your tasks and fully implement the plant recipes.



Exclusive Features:
- Special Production Recipes for Your Plants
- 24-Hour Digital Assistant
- Add Unlimited Photos
- Production Planning
- Detection of Diseases from Photos with Artificial Intelligence
